    • Field Detail

      • SELECTION_QUEUE_NAME

        static final java.lang.String SELECTION_QUEUE_NAME
        SELECTION_QUEUE_NAME is the in-memory queue for publishing and subscribing the selection model updates. For the implementation, it's the ZK event queue name to be looked up from org.zkoss.zk.ui.event.EventQueues.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
